Detailed Description

Keyword definition object.

Struct which is used to define a keyword. In gParse a keyword is a token, which fits the criteria for a tIdentifier token (see: gTokenType_e), that matches one of the token members of a list of gKeyword structs. A list of these structs must be terminated with an entry containing a NULL "token" member.
